Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Dibua Elementary School in Barangay Dibua, City of Laoag, to Don Galicano R. Rafales Memorial Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 215
An Act Changing the Name of the Dibua Elementary School in Barangay Dibua, City of Laoag, to Don Galicano R. Rafales Memorial Elementary School
Section 1. The name of the Dibua Elementary School in Barangay Dibua, City of Laoag, is hereby changed to Don Galicano R. Rafales Memorial Elementary School.1Ã¢wphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: March 25, 1982
